<p style="text-align: justify"><br /><br />
Obviously some flipped images had to be eliminated because the flipped version didnâ€™t quite look right (see the 4 below), while in some others, some manual changes were necessary (the dot of the flipped 9 had to be moved to the top):</p>

<p><img src="/agneev-blog/assets/img/img_1_29.png?raw=true" alt="Image_29" width="125&quot;, height=&quot;100" />Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â 
