<p style="text-align: justify"><br /><br />
Unfortunately, no sensible flips are possible for the numbers 7 and 8, and so these therefore need to be augmented in a different way. I manually added an â€˜iâ€™ to viiâ€™s and removed an â€˜iâ€™ from viiiâ€™s, as shown below (original to the right in each pair). While effective, this method was laborious and time-consuming, taking me over half an hour to generate a hundred images.</p>

<p><img src="/agneev-blog/assets/img/img_1_32.png?raw=true" alt="Image_32" width="150&quot;, height=&quot;125" />
<img src="/agneev-blog/assets/img/img_1_33.png?raw=true" alt="Image_33" width="150&quot;, height=&quot;125" />
