<p style="text-align: justify"><br /><br />
As can be seen, the results obtained were passable copies of the numbers, without being so realistic as to eliminate the need for real data. The random addition of noise and dilation made some samples unusable â€“ these I discarded and created fresh samples in their place. Examples:</p>

<p><img src="/agneev-blog/assets/img/img_1_63.png?raw=true" alt="Image_63" width="125&quot;, height=&quot;100" />Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â 
